Kapil sets off the fireworks of laughs and jokes as Bittu's brother, Sittu, who has come to ask for his share of the property. Sittu starts his one liners and wise cracks on the various fights and feuds for property. Sittu then asks the audience to share their views on any kinds of fights in their homes. Sittu then starts shouting for Bittu but Bittu's wife steps out and a laugh riot follows. Hearing the commotion, Bua steps out to inquire about the same. Later, Ravi Kishen, Manoj Tiwari and Nirahua join Kapil on the stage. Watch the episode and have a laugh of your life.

Already famous for his amazing comic timing and his talent to dig humor out of any situation, he is ready present everyday life in a fresh ad unique way.
